org.archive.wayback.archivalurl

Class ArchivalUrlDateRedirectingClosestResultSelector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.wayback.replay.DateRedirectingClosestResultSelector
      • org.archive.wayback.archivalurl.ArchivalUrlDateRedirectingClosestResultSelector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClosestResultSelector
    Deprecated. 
    1.8.1 2014-07-2 no replacement. use DefaultClosestResultSelector.

    public class ArchivalUrlDateRedirectingClosestResultSelector
extends DateRedirectingClosestResultSelector
    ClosestResultSelector that redirects to Archival-URL replay URL for the capture given if its timestamp is different from the request.

    This class preserves context flag upon redirect, but can cause redirect loop.
